Listing Typescript makes it a very strong area to consider.

text: VNUHCM - University of Science Ho Chi Minh, Vietnam
description: This area is weak because the expected graduation date is in the future (2027) but it indicates only having frontend roles. The candidate should aim to get internship as a fullstack engineer instead.

This section is weak because it only showcases frontend projects. The job description emphasizes C#, .NET, and SQL, which are primarily backend technologies. To improve, the candidate should include personal projects or contributions to open-source projects that demonstrate proficiency in these technologies. It's important to demonstrate skills relevant to the specific requirements of the job.

This area is weak because it lacks any mention of skills in .NET, C#, SQL, SSRS, or database technologies, which are core requirements for the job. The candidate should either acquire these skills or explicitly state a willingness to learn them. Even mentioning familiarity with SQL would be an improvement.
